{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","title":"热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367057,"created":1780371330024,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"08ed6934ea9e8121d9fa63dbe86a9533","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.prn_tune串口调参命令","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":12,"offset":356},"end":{"line":21,"column":52,"offset":396},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.prn_tune串口调参命令"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.打印机参数排列组合记录","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":14,"offset":412},"end":{"line":22,"column":51,"offset":449},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.打印机参数排列组合记录"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.prn_tune串口调参命令","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":3,"offset":2739},"end":{"line":111,"column":43,"offset":2779},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.prn_tune串口调参命令"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.打印机参数排列组合记录","position":{"start":{"line":112,"column":3,"offset":2798},"end":{"line":112,"column":40,"offset":2835},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.打印机参数排列组合记录"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-07_热敏打印机驱动算法分析与工作记录","id":"0a6f1fae03382ed23a61e4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.B